data.description: Location, location, location! This townhome is conveniently located close to Woodmen and I25. This sought after community features walk paths, community pool and easy living. This townhome is located on the edge of the community. There is two bedrooms with vaulted ceilings and two ensuite bathrooms. With newly renovated kitchen, new hot water heater, new carpet, new paint and accent walls - you will want to see this cute property yourself. HOA takes care of trash & refuse, water bill, snow removal, pool and pool maintenance, exterior maintenance, ground maintenance of common spaces and insurance. Welcome home to one of Colorado's Finest.
